---
title: Easy Southern Crumbed Chicken & Peri Peri Mayo with Butter Corn Rice & Apple Slaw
description: You can’t go wrong with a crumbed chicken feast, especially paired with a buttery corn rice and a sweet-and-crisp apple slaw! This one has our smokey All-American spice cooked right into the crunchy crumb. The only thing that could make it better is an epic dipping sauce - oh wait, we’ve got that too!
